WEBVTT

00:04:28.360 --> 00:04:31.376
He was staring past me
and just kind of looking at the ground.

00:04:31.400 --> 00:04:32.656
I gave him a ginger ale

00:04:32.680 --> 00:04:35.296
and just started talking
about nothing in particular,

00:04:35.320 --> 00:04:39.240
but as I was talking,
he sneezed from the ginger ale.

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:43.616
And the sneeze --
it jerked his body upright,

00:04:43.640 --> 00:04:45.576
sparking him back to life a little bit.

00:04:45.600 --> 00:04:50.776
And he just kept drinking and sneezing
and sparking, over and over and over again

00:04:50.800 --> 00:04:52.360
until it stopped.

00:04:53.280 --> 00:04:54.480
And I heard,

00:04:55.440 --> 00:04:57.296
"Heheheheheh,

00:04:57.320 --> 00:05:00.056
heheheheheh ...